Syria Arrests Gunmen in Deraa, Foils Bombing Plot, SANA Says

-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 
2011-09-22T08:08:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/syria-arrests-gunmen-in-deraa-foils-bombing-plot-sana-says.html
Syrian officials arrested a group
of gunmen in the city of Deraa after discovering large
quantities of bombs, the state-run Syrian Arab News Agency
 reported  today.  The suspects planned to use the explosives to attack crowds
of civilians, SANA said. Clashes between security forces and
gunmen in the city of Homs left three officers injured,
according to the agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in  Abu Dhabi  at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 